  n   (   t   [   o   ]   )   :   t   [   o   ]   ;   r   e   t   u   r   n       e   }   ,   o   =   A   r   r   a   y   .   i   s   A   r   r   a   y   |   |   f   u   n   c   t   i   o   n   (   t   )   {   r   e   t   u   r   n   "   [   o   b   j   e   c   t       A   r   r   a   y   ]   "   =   =   =   O   b   j   e   c   t   .   p   r   o   t   o   t   y   p   e   .   t   o   S   t   r   i   n   g   .   c   a   l   l   (   t   )   }   ,   e   =   {   }   ,   l   =   /   ^   .   *   \   .   .   *   $   /   ,   i   =   f   u   n   c   t   i   o   n   (   t   )   {   i   f   (   t   )   {   i   f   (   "   f   u   n   c   t   i   o   n   "   =   =   t   y   p   e   o   f       t   )   t   h   r   o   w   "   G   l   b   l       i   s   n   '   t       m   e   a   n   t       t   o       s   t   o   r   e       f   u   n   c   t   i   o   n   s   ,       y   o   "   ;   i   f   (   o   (   t   )   )   f   o   r   (   v   a   r       n   =   0   ,   e   =   t   .   l   e   n   g   t   h   ;   e   &gt;   n   ;   n   +   +   )   i   (   t   [   n   ]   )   ;   e   l   s   e       i   f   (   r   (   t   )   )   f   o   r   (   v   a   r       n       i   n       t   )   i   (   t   [   n   ]   )   }   }   ;   t   .
